{
    "a_galaxy_workflow": "true",
    "annotation": "Automated workflow to validate Galaxy endpoint reliability using daily test runs of Falco and Bowtie2 via the SABER package. Designed for lightweight, scalable monitoring across multiple instances.",
    "comments": [],
    "creator": [
